y can blame you as you have helped more than could be expected already.                                                                                                                                        |Such a kind and generous offer goes above and beyond the call of duty.  Each member gains +15000 prestige and gains a level.                                                                                                                                   îYou enter the great hall.  There is really little of interest here.  It is filled with common folk who come here to talk and swap tales of interest.                                                                                                           bSuch a kind and generous offer goes above and beyond the call of duty.  Each member gains a level.                                                                                                                                                             jSuch a kind and generous offer goes above and beyond the call of duty.  Each member gains +15000 prestige.                                                                                                                                                     ≠A locked door and it is in good repair.  You smell the odor of a large unwashed body on the other side of the door.  Whatever or whoever is beyond is large and most unclean.                                                                                  UA large monastery.  The brotherhood is more than willing to attend to all your needs.                                                                                                                                                                          ±Do you wish to skip the scrolling text of this story?  You may still view it this text at any time by selecting "Tale Of The Mithril Vault" from the Maps/Notes menu at any time.                                                                              